      <title>杰富瑞牵头的银行集团为标签制造商提供更优惠的贷款条件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/jefferies-led-bank-group-sweetens-terms-on-loan-for-label-maker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由杰富瑞金融集团 (Jefferies Financial Group Inc.) 牵头的多家银行提高了拟向 M2S Group Intermediate Holdings Inc. 提供的 8.7 亿美元杠杆贷款的条款，但本月初该贷款未能按计划定价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/jefferies-led-bank-group-sweetens-terms-on-loan-for-label-maker</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 15:14:32 GMT</pubDate>
