      <title>德克萨斯州干旱迫使小镇拖欠供水系统债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/texas-drought-forces-small-town-to-default-on-water-system-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州持续的干旱正在损害一个小镇的财政状况，使其无法向债券持有人偿还债务，这是罕见的气候相关违约情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/texas-drought-forces-small-town-to-default-on-water-system-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 15:06:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
