    <item>
      <title>7-Eleven 和 Pop Tarts 掀起并购热潮，夏季促销活动火爆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/summer-dealmaking-heats-up-as-7-eleven-pop-tarts-drive-m-a-wave</link>
      <description><![CDATA[消费品行业的两笔巨额交易让银行家们在通常平静的夏季忙碌不已，这表明企业界的信心不断增强，这有助于延续交易复苏的势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/summer-dealmaking-heats-up-as-7-eleven-pop-tarts-drive-m-a-wave</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 12:30:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
